---
<section class="global-contact-wrapper mt-3 mb-3">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-card glass shadow-lg">
      <div class="contact-text">
        <h2>Une urgence ou un projet ?</h2>
        <p>Contactez-nous directement ou laissez vos coordonnées pour être rappelé immédiatement.</p>
        <a href="tel:+32465767511" class="btn btn-accent btn-large pulse-animation mt-1 mb-2" style="display: inline-block;">
          📞 Appeler le 0465 76 75 11
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-form-container">
        <form action="https://formsubmit.co/midebzn@gmail.com" method="POST" class="global-form">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Nouveau contact depuis le site web Fbaleste !">
          <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">
          
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Votre Nom / Entreprise" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <input type="tel" name="phone" required placeholder="Votre Numéro de Téléphone" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <textarea name="message" rows="3" required placeholder="Décrivez votre problème (ex: Fuite d'eau, chaudière en panne...)"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Demander une intervention</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .shadow-lg {
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 76, 129, 0.1);
  }
  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98) 0%, rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.95) 100%);
    border: 2px solid rgba(15, 76, 129, 0.1);
  }
  .contact-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
  }
  .contact-text h2 { color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .contact-form-container {
    flex: 1.5;
    min-width: 300px;
  }
  .form-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .form-group {
    flex: 1;
  }
  .global-form input, .global-form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    background-color: var(--white);
  }
  .global-form input:focus, .global-form textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 76, 129, 0.1);
  }
  .w-100 { 
    width: 100%; 
    padding: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .form-row {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
